flowchart TD
    Bench[("Benchmark Harness\n(Kafka-delta)")]
    
    %% Injection
    Bench -->|1. Inject Audio| T1[Topic: audio.ingress]
    
    %% Processing Chain
    T1 --> S1[ASR Service]
    S1 -->|2. Produce Text| T2[Topic: asr.text]
    T2 --> S2[Translation Service]
    S2 -->|3. Produce Trans| T3[Topic: translation.text]
    
    %% Measurement (The Spy)
    T1 -.->|Timestamp T0| Bench
    T2 -.->|Timestamp T1| Bench
    T3 -.->|Timestamp T2| Bench
    
    %% Metrics
    Bench -->|Calculate| Metrics["Latency Metrics\n(T2 - T0 = E2E Latency)"]

    style Bench fill:#ffecb3,stroke:#ff6f00
    style Metrics fill:#dcedc8,stroke:#558b2f